create a calculator application with basic operation like + - / * and write some Test Cases using junit, hamcrust and mockito.
Application must have these checkpoints.
1. Write test case for check exeception in calculator.
2. create calculator service class with different other service like add service
   so that application can perform test without using real service.
3. for the comparasion actual result must have to use hamecrust library instead of junit
4. only use junit annotation for testcase 
5. follow the text-fixture style in writing test cases.
6. Application must have 
   a. Runner class
   b. Suite class
   c. and least 4 test case for each basic operation ( + - / * )
7. Test case can perform multiple test on each operation 
   a. with interger
   b. double
   c. float 

